    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>目前有部分玩家反馈，官方中文与某些民间汉化 MOD/补丁可能会产生轻微冲突，导致字体缺失或显示异常。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果大家遇到类似情况，可以尝试暂时关闭相关汉化 MOD，并删除可能残留的旧文件。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/dd5a8a0d4abde876a1ea56d64f75a418.avif?t=1770868510\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你穿透寒冷的雾霭，大地在脚下缓缓苏醒。荒野低语，废墟呼吸，古老的凯尔特灵影正潜伏在树影与石碑之后。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不是命定的英雄，却将亲手铸造史诗。探索荒蛮世界的伤痕，见证禁忌生灵的轮廓，让每一次抉择都在命运的洪流中激起涟漪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/a8dad272f73b34ed83afcb0dc51e17b6.poster.avif?t=1770868510\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/a8dad272f73b34ed83afcb0dc51e17b6.webm?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/a8dad272f73b34ed83afcb0dc51e17b6.mp4?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这是你的旅程，这是你的战斗——这是你的传奇。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/4f0637d9c0c6e1b740990647d4d0bc88.avif?t=1770868510\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两面旗帜在风中猎猎作响：一方守护自然与灵魂的律法，一方以铁血与秩序重铸世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盟友的誓言，如利刃般锋利；阴影中的背叛，也从未远离。你必须决定站在谁的身旁……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/b69484f4e2bf4d5b8ebe059fbb89fc75.poster.avif?t=1770868510\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/b69484f4e2bf4d5b8ebe059fbb89fc75.webm?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/b69484f4e2bf4d5b8ebe059fbb89fc75.mp4?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你做出的每一次选择，都会让这片土地震颤。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/4a98bb9df1060b2745af888c1dda0fc3.avif?t=1770868510\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从尘埃中起步，在风暴般的世界里步步前行。废弃城镇、沉眠圣坛、被遗忘的矿坑与破碎古堡皆在前方等待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可用钢铁与鲜血谱写战斗乐章，也可追随蛛丝线索，发掘掩埋至今的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/1f1cde74d7798aa00c35a8ac9bfdd7dd.poster.avif?t=1770868510\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/1f1cde74d7798aa00c35a8ac9bfdd7dd.webm?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/1f1cde74d7798aa00c35a8ac9bfdd7dd.mp4?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>唯有勇气与智慧，方能揭开这片土地的面纱。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/8b2e2ce50d2714501a8f80a19cbc8826.avif?t=1770868510\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深林、荒野与海风之下，皆潜藏古老灵体的足迹。牠们支配元素、情绪与生命，并与世界同呼吸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以封印它们、奴役它们，或与它们缔结契约，但必须承受等价的怒火与代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/03dbcd68f9fe1537625bcd4dc7f722a3.poster.avif?t=1770868510\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/03dbcd68f9fe1537625bcd4dc7f722a3.webm?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/03dbcd68f9fe1537625bcd4dc7f722a3.mp4?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>当灵魂的力量觉醒，大地本身都会记住你的名字。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/80fff9560c937bef9d9222a9a984ddd3.poster.avif?t=1770868510\" width=600 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585180/extras/80fff9560c937bef9d9222a9a984ddd3.webm?t=1770868510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>异乡人，当世界注视你的抉择——</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> 你会成为自然法则的掌控者，</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> 还是铺展在祭坛上的祭品？</strong></p>",
